high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge then turn right and walk to the stove then take a step left.
Pick up the knife that's to the left of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the counter.
Cut the apple into three chunks.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave and close the door.
Go back to where you cut up the apple.
Pick up a chunk of apple.
Go back to the microwave.
Warm the chunk of apple in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the fridge that will be on your right then turn right to face it when you get to it.
Put the apple chunk in the freezer.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot chunk of apple in the freezer.

high_descs: Move to the stand at the narrow strip of counter between the stove and window.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Turn around the carry the knife to the kitchen island, so you're standing in front of an apple and pepper grinder.
Slice the apple with the knife.
Carry the knife around the island to the microwave.
Place the knife on the plate inside the microwave.
Turn around and go back to the apple on the other side of the island.
Pick up a slice of apple from the island.
Carry the apple slice to the microwave.
Place the apple slice in the microwave, turn it  on, and then remove once heated.
Carry the apple slice to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple slice in the top section.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved apple slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the oven, turn left, and face the counter beside the stove.
Pick up the knife.
Turn around and walk to the counter.
Slice the apple on the counter.
Turn right, walk to the wall, turn left, and walk to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, walk to the end of the counter, and turn right.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Turn right, walk to the wall, turn left, and walk to the microwave.
Put the slice of apple in the microwave, heat the slice of apple, and pick up the apple in the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the slice of apple in the freezer, and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot slice of apple in the freezer.
